author: @diemmy4417
text: It's been so fast that 1 year has passed since the album 'ME' was released. I still remember when Jisoo posted a photo on Instagram with the words 'coming soon', my heart felt very happy and very proud at that time. about her because after 7 years of debuting with BLACKPINK, she found herself a new color and a new direction. At that time, I felt like I wanted to cry. I looked forward every day and every hour to wait for her MV. I remember when the MV was released it was at 11am (Vietnam time is 2 hours later than Korea). I was still studying at school and I hadn't finished school yet. I was waiting for the clock to peak at 11am and I had to watching Jisoo's MV live, the feeling I had at that time now when I think about it, it's still impossible to describe that feeling. I've been waiting for nearly 7 years and today it's been 1 year since the album 'ME' was released. Sometimes I suddenly think that BLACKPINK's Jisoo has already made her solo debut? I couldn't believe it was true until I watched her MV 'FLOWER' again and I believed it was true it wasn't the dream I had been dreaming for so long and finally a few words I want to say To my sister Jisoo, I hope that now and in the future you will always do what you want to do, do what you have spent all your time trying to have a JISOO today, congratulations on the album. 'ME' has turned 1 year old

author: @tulinyildirim1779
text:
Un poco de información sobre 'FLOWER' y 'ALL EYES ON ME', también sobre el vídeo musical de 'FLOWER' y su coreografía. 

La identidad de Jisoo como solista está en pleno florecimiento con la canción principal 'FLOWER'. Se agregó un arreglo mínimo al sonido único del bajo. La letra lírica y la línea melódica se mezclan armoniosamente con la voz única de Jisoo.

'All Eyes On Me' muestra la habilidad vocal de Jisoo. Es una canción que se destaca con un sonido de batería vivo agregado a una guitarra y un bajo reales, y una línea principal letal. 

El video musical de "FLOWER", con el mayor costo de producción en la historia de BLACKPINK, fue filmado con una cámara de cine para todas las locaciones en los EE. UU. 

La presentación de 'FLOWER' también es de gran interés. Se espera que el tema de la canción reviva dinámicamente con una coreografía colorida que encarna flores y mariposas, haciendo que sea imposible quitar la vista ni por un momento.

author: @xinjiezou
text:
OMG!!! 水墨画Chinese ink-wash painting，梅花Mei flower，中式屏风Chinese style screen~！As a Chinese fan, I was so moved by the Chinese cultural elements in this visual film！😭These elements appear in all corners of my life. For example, in Hangzhou, there are even Chinese screens at the entrance of some bathroom .  🤣The Mei flower(plum blossom) is one of the "Four Gentlemen" (四君子) of China (the others being the chrysanthemum/JU flower , the orchid/LAN flower, and bamboo/Yes, it's the same plant that pandas eat.). Since I was a child, I have learned many poems about Mei flower, and I can recite them anytime. Ink painting is also something you can learn as a hobby in school ~ that's why I can recognize these as Chinese cultural elements, they are everywhere in my life ~ 
Love you，Jisoo！Thank you for loving Chinese culture and actively spreading it, love you~ She is a Korean but she is spreading Chinese culture.I'm excited to see that~She is a real-Chinese Cultural Communicator！♥
PS：The world needs a variety of different voices. Don't always delete my replies, I just want to show my love.♥

author: @xinjiezou
text:
OMG!!! 水墨画Chinese ink-wash painting，梅花Mei flower，中式屏风Chinese style screen~！As a Chinese fan, I was so moved by the Chinese cultural elements in this visual film！😭These elements appear in all corners of my life. For example, in Hangzhou, there are even Chinese screens at the entrance of some bathroom .  🤣The Mei flower(plum blossom) is one of the "Four Gentlemen" (四君子) of China (the others being the chrysanthemum/JU flower , the orchid/LAN flower, and bamboo/Yes, it's the same plant that pandas eat.). Since I was a child, I have learned many poems about Mei flower, and I can recite them anytime. Ink painting is also something you can learn as a hobby in school ~ that's why I can recognize these as Chinese cultural elements, they are everywhere in my life ~ 
Love you，Jisoo！Thank you for loving Chinese culture and actively spreading it, love you~ She is a Korean but she is spreading Chinese culture.I'm excited to see that~She is a real-Chinese Cultural Communicator！♥
PS：The world needs a variety of different voices. Don't always delete my replies, I just want to show my love.♥

this is a general streaming tutorial 
for youtube:
-Dont skip adds (if they are too long, you can skip after 31 seconds. thats when a commercial counted as seen and adds to the total video view).
-watch 2-3 short other videos after you finished the MV
-search for the MV in the YT search bar and click the MV
-dont stop streaming after 1 or 2 hours(this is when the stream always rapitaly slowing down. seen in the previous comebacks.)

author: @copiaka
text:
감사합니다! 부다페스트는 헝가리의 수도이며, 동유럽에서 가장 아름다운 도시 중 하나로 꼽힙니다.

부다페스트는 두 개의 도시인 부다(Buda)와 페스트(Pest)가 합쳐져서 만들어진 이름으로, 도시를 분할하는 도나우강과 비슷한 다리로 연결되어 있습니다. 이 도시는 오스트리아-헝가리 제국의 영향으로 인해 유럽 다른 도시들과는 다른 독특한 분위기를 가지고 있습니다.

부다페스트에는 다양한 명소와 유적지가 있습니다. 예를 들면, 비치 성당(Buda Castle)과 마트라셔터 궁전(Matthias Church) 같은 중세 유적지와 히로쇼 궁전(Heroes' Square), 세인트 스테판 대성당(St. Stephen's Basilica) 등의 바로크 양식의 건축물이 있습니다. 또한, 부다페스트는 유럽에서 가장 큰 온천도시 중 하나로, 그 수많은 온천과 목욕탕으로 유명합니다.

부다페스트는 또한 다양한 문화적 행사와 축제를 개최하며, 헝가리 음식과 와인도 유명합니다. 도시 전체가 밤에 빛나는 야경과 함께, 낭만적이고 흥미로운 여행을 즐길 수 있는 곳입니다.
